# Trivy ignore list: CVEs accepted or without an upstream fix.
#
# The Trivy step already passes ignore-unfixed, so vulnerabilities with no
# available patch in the base image (python:3.14-slim) do not fail the build.
# Add a CVE id below only when a fixable HIGH/CRITICAL needs a temporary,
# documented exception while a base image bump is pending. Review periodically.
#
# Example:
# CVE-2025-12345  # accepted YYYY-MM-DD, no fix in slim base, low real impact
